.Dd June 26, 2026
.Dt LIBVSLVM 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm libvslvm.h
.Nd Library to access the Linux Logical Volume Manager (LVM) volume system
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In libvslvm.h
.Pp
